                    </div>
                    <span>This is a very poorly put together book. It's organized as a series of small articles, but the article sizes vary widely and many of them contradict others. ... <br>It definately has some useful information in there, but it's tough to extract through the poor organization and formatting. </span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">An excellent compilation of useful shaders</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
